                            What is the Co-op Work Permit?
                        </a>
                    </h3>
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Accordion Body -->
                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1583183470166-what-is-the-co-op-work-permit-" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1583183470166-what-is-the-co-op-work-permit-">
                    <div class="panel-body ">
                        <div class="1583183470166 stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="a3c9d7b3-5541-46a9-8ad7-93cc8abb89b8" >

    <p>It is a required document for international students who will be completing a co-op work opportunity or placement period. This permit allows international students to work full-time during regular academic sessions.&nbsp;</p>
    





</div>
