                            When should students apply for a Co-op Work Permit?
                        </a>
                    </h3>
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Accordion Body -->
                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1583183474565-when-should-students-apply-for-a-co-op-work-permit-" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1583183474565-when-should-students-apply-for-a-co-op-work-permit-">
                    <div class="panel-body ">
                        <div class="1583183474565 stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="ffcc11bf-e7f2-4272-8bd2-cd585d670b8b" >

    <p>Students should apply prior to the work term. Our recommendation is that students apply as soon as they know they will be completing a co-op work term or placement opportunity. The IRCC processing times fluctuate quite often (as often as weekly), however, recently we have been seeing processing times of 3 or more months.</p>
    





</div>
