    <p>We strongly recommend that you encourage students to attend our<a href="https://connectru.ryerson.ca/organization/iss/events"> Immigration Insights group advising sessions.</a> These sessions are offered monthly covering various immigration applications including the co-op work permit. Students will leave these sessions with strong knowledge of how to apply for the permit and consequently greater confidence in working on and submitting their application to IRCC. </p>
    





